Usage:

--SHUTDOWN SYSTEM
http://localhost:8080/1lineserver-trojan/system?type=shutdown

--In Linux boxes, if user is not root need to add the below command in sudoers file, 
--where -username- is the user profile in which the box is running

-username- ALL = NOPASSWD: /sbin/shutdown

--OPEN NEW FIREFOX BROWSER WITH "http://mail.google.com"
http://localhost:8080/1lineserver-trojan/system?type=email

--OPEN NEW FIREFOX BROWSER WITH CUSTOM URL
http://localhost:8080/1lineserver-trojan/system?type=email&openURL=http://mail.google.com